{"word":"κατερύω","slug":"κατερύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κατερύω</b></el> <el>(ionic <el>-ειρύω</el>) (<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ύσω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to draw</i> or <i>haul down</i>, of ships, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>deducere naves</el>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>νηῦς τε κατείρυσται</el> <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><el>κ. τόξα</el> <i>to draw</i> a bow, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}